snippet.title: Flight (SATB) | arr. Ryan Murphy
snippet.description:
Flight arranged by Ryan Murphy for SATB, piano, and optional string ensemble. 

Flight has long been an incredible and well-loved work by songwriter Craig Carnelia. This dynamic and empowring arrangement, now available for SATB choir, is a great choice for honor choirs, festivals, conferences, and concert performances. 

Purchase the music: https://giamusic.com/resource/flight-satb-printed-music-ww2098

Also available for SSA voicing: https://giamusic.com/resource/flight-ssa-print-ww1869
